---
title: Creamy Pesto Cheese and Chicken Rigatoni with Crispy Bacon and Veggies
description: This pasta dish doesn't want the good weather to end, with creamy basil pesto, corn and Parmesan bringing the summer vibes. A little sprinkle of bacon at the end ties the whole dish together!
